    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all fuel stations to sell HVO",
        "additional_details": "We think this will help the UK to reduce the net CO2 emissions, while reducing the reliance on the volatile and heavily politicised oil markets.",
        "background": "Government to mandate that HVO (Hydrotreated Vegetable Oil) must be available at the pump as a suitable alternative to diesel. This is already available at a handful of fuel forecourts in the UK, which provides a greener and cleaner alternative to diesel.",
